### Test Map Endpoints
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1

### 1. Get Map Pins (GeoJSON)
### Returns all non-closed reports as GeoJSON FeatureCollection
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/pins
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Map Pins for Specific Agency
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/pins?agencyId=YOUR_AGENCY_ID
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Heatmap Data (Default: Last 30 days, Indonesia bounds)
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/heatmap
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Heatmap Data for Specific Region (Bandung area)
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/heatmap?minLat=-7.0&minLng=107.5&maxLat=-6.8&maxLng=107.7&days=30
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Heatmap Data for Last 90 Days
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/heatmap?days=90
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get Clustered Data (Zoom level 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/cluster?zoom=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get Clustered Data for Specific Region (Bandung, Zoom 12)
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/cluster?zoom=12&minLat=-7.0&minLng=107.5&maxLat=-6.8&maxLng=107.7
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get Clustered Data (Low Zoom - Province Level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/map/cluster?zoom=8&minLat=-7.5&minLng=107.0&maxLat=-6.5&maxLng=108.0
Content-Type: application/json

