### Notes:
# - All endpoints are cached (pins: 30s, heatmap: 5min, cluster: 1min)
# - GeoJSON coordinates are [longitude, latitude] (not lat, lng!)
# - Heatmap uses ~1km grid cells (0.01 degrees)
# - Cluster grid size varies by zoom level
# - Max 2000 pins, 1000 heatmap points, 500 clusters
